WEBVTT

00:02:28.360 --> 00:02:31.976
then all the fools in the world,
no actually,

00:02:32.000 --> 00:02:35.776
all the wise people in the world,
would attain happiness

00:02:35.800 --> 00:02:37.762
because the foolish are happy anyway.

00:02:37.810 --> 00:02:40.960
(Laughter and applause)

00:02:40.960 --> 00:02:45.230
They are so happy that if something small
triggers unhappiness, they get furious.

00:02:46.080 --> 00:02:49.896
But well, this issue
of laughter is complicated.

00:02:49.920 --> 00:02:51.616
Because whenever someone laughs,

00:02:51.640 --> 00:02:55.696
there is someone who is turning
green with envy.

00:02:55.720 --> 00:02:57.530
Now let me share an incident with you.

00:02:57.554 --> 00:03:00.576
So there was a priest and a priestess.